OL,3,C'Wales has become a hub for cyber
OL,4,Csecurity' says industry expert
OL,6,FFfion Gruffudd who grew up in the
OL,7,FGwendraeth Valley in Carmarthenshire
OL,8,Fis regarded as one of the world's
OL,9,Fleading cyber security lawyers.
OL,11,FFfion says the risk of cyber attacks
OL,12,Fhas "exploded", and continues to
OL,13,Fworsen. She says that the use of
OL,14,Fransomware, a tool used by criminals
OL,15,Fto lock up a company's systems and
OL,16,Fsteal data, has become "a huge thing
OL,17,Fin the last few years."
