OL,4,Csecurity' says industry expert
OL,6,FWhen asked on Face to Face about how
OL,7,Fprepared Wales is against cyber
OL,8,Fthreats, Ffion said that "I think
OL,9,Fpeople are aware of the risks and are
OL,10,Ftaking the risks seriously... the next
OL,11,Fstep is making sure we have our
OL,12,Fdefences in place."
OL,14,FShe added that "in fact Wales has
OL,15,Fbecome a hub for cyber defence and
OL,16,Fcyber security. From the point of view
OL,17,Fof encouraging cyber skills amongst
OL,18,Fyoung people".
