OL,3,C'Wales has become a hub for cyber
OL,4,Csecurity' says industry expert
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government announced a cyber
OL,7,Faction plan in May 2023 to encourage
OL,8,Fcollaboration in the industry on jobs,
OL,9,Fskills and security.
OL,11,FThe minister behind the plan, Vaughan
OL,12,FGething MS said a key aim is
OL,13,Fencouraging more younger people into
OL,14,Fthe sector.
OL,16,F"We are committed to shaping a more
OL,17,Fdiverse sector that is driven by
OL,18,Ftalent and not held back by glass
OL,19,Fceilings and Wales already sets strong
OL,20,Fexample with one of the most active
OL,21,F'Women in Cyber clusters' in the UK.
