OL,3,C'Wales has become a hub for cyber
OL,4,Csecurity' says industry expert
OL,6,F"The innovation across our sector
OL,7,Fmakes Wales an attractive offer for
OL,8,Fthose working in cyber and a great
OL,9,Fplace to build businesses in the
OL,10,Findustry. As well as creating
OL,11,Fopportunities and jobs, it stimulates
OL,12,Fthe development of cyber skills which
OL,13,Fin turn makes our businesses and
OL,14,Fpublic services more resilient to
OL,15,Fcyber threats."
OL,17,FAfter studying Law and Politics, Ffion
OL,18,Ftook on a job at a law firm in London.
