OL,6,FShe worked with various major banks
OL,7,Finvestigating computer fraud. It was
OL,8,Fthis experience that really got her
OL,9,Finterested in this element of the law
OL,10,Fand cyber security in particular.
OL,12,FWhen discussing the life of a high-
OL,13,Fflying lawyer, Ffion talked about the
OL,14,Fstresses and challenges that come with
OL,15,Fthe job.
OL,17,FEspecially in the early years of a
OL,18,Fyoung lawyer's career, as they try to
OL,19,Festablish themselves within their
OL,20,Ffield. She recalled "working all
OL,21,Fhours" during her 20s.
