OL,6,FOften "working all-nighters, as I had
OL,7,Fa pillow under my desk. The cleaners
OL,8,Fwould wake me up in the morning" when
OL,9,Fshe would fall asleep at her desk.
OL,11,FIt was during these years as a lawyer
OL,12,Fthat her dad gave her the advice to
OL,13,Ffind the right balance in life. Ffion
OL,14,Fdidn't necessarily see this as a
OL,15,Fwarning to slow down, but to "find
OL,16,Fother things that bring me joy".
